nest g mo modules/auth --flat --no-spec
nest g mo modules/database --flat --no-spec
nest g mo api --no-spec

nest g module api/products --no-spec
nest g controller api/products --no-spec
nest g service api/products --flat --no-spec
nest g interface api/products/products --flat --no-spec

Instalar mongoose
$ npm install --save @nestjs/mongoose mongoose
$ npm install --save-dev @types/mongoose

Instalar Bcrypt
$ npm install @types/bcrypt bcrypt

Passport Local
$ npm install --save @nestjs/passport passport passport-local
$ npm install --save-dev @types/passport-local

Configurar JWT
$ npm install --save @nestjs/jwt passport-jwt
$ npm install --save-dev @types/passport-jwt

Modulo usuarios
$ nest g module modules/auth/users
$ nest g service modules/auth/users
$ nest g controller modules/auth/users
$ nest g interface modules/auth/users/users

Agregar el config module
$ npm i --save @nestjs/config
